Class SimpleHashtable.TableEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • hr.fer.zemris.java.tecaj.hw4.collections.SimpleHashtable.TableEntry
  • Enclosing class:
    SimpleHashtable

    public static class SimpleHashtable.TableEntry
extends java.lang.Object
    Class which represents a single key-value entry in hash table. While value can be changed at will, key can only be assigned upon creation of an object from this class.
    Author:
    Domagoj Lateƒçki
